  "title": "Customer Acquisition Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title:</strong> Brand Ambassador – Customer Acquisition (Roadshow)<br>\n <strong>Location:</strong> Island-wide / Multiple Branches</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>About the Role:</strong><br>\nOur client is looking for motivated Brand Ambassadors to drive customer engagement and acquisition across various locations. This role involves marketing banking products directly to customers at roadshows, branch activations, and community events.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Promote and market banking products to potential customers across island-wide locations.</li>\n  <li>Represent the company at roadshows, branch activations, and events.</li>\n  <li>Build relationships with potential customers and drive acquisition targets.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with marketing and sales teams to execute campaigns effectively.</li>\n  <li>Report performance metrics and provide feedback to improve engagement strategies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum <strong>N-level qualification with at least 3 passes</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Able to <strong>communicate fluently in English</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal skills; confident engaging with diverse audiences.</li>\n  <li>Target-driven, self-motivated, and resilient in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n  <li>Willing and able to travel across multiple locations as required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What’s on Offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive salary with performance-based incentives.</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to engage with diverse customer segments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We appreciate your interest and look forward to reviewing your application. Due to high application volume, only shortlisted candidates will be contacted — thank you for your understanding!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>WeCruit Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel: Tan Soon Hock (Steven) | Registration No. R1109889</p>",
